id: Soul papers are mystical scrolls, extraordinarily unique, and there are two types: Soul Papers and Soul Dark Papers. In other words, the Soul Scroll and its dark version. These scrolls reveal the likes and dislikes of the dolls. We'll start with the normal scroll. Apply the scroll to the doll.

id: Good job, lastly, light the fireplace.

Before you go, I want to clarify that in this game mode, you can return to the refuge by driving the caravan. Lastly, what we've done with Lil in this mode will need to be done for each of the dolls to identify the impostor. Keep in mind that the campaign mode is intended to be a co-op experience in the future, which is why it's important that it isn't brief or quick. Each case could take you days to solve, but it's asynchronous, meaning you can exit whenever you want and continue playing later, and everything will remain as you left it.
str: Sebelum Anda pergi, saya ingin menjelaskan bahwa dalam mode permainan ini, Anda dapat kembali ke perlindungan dengan mengemudikan karavan. Terakhir, apa yang telah kita lakukan dengan Lil dalam mode ini perlu dilakukan untuk setiap boneka untuk mengidentifikasi penipu.

id: Doll Who is a deduction board game where two players try to guess the identity of the character chosen by their opponent. Each player has a board with a series of characters with different traits. By asking yes or no questions about the characters' features (such as whether they have a hat or appeared in the daycare map), players eliminate options until they discover the opponent's character. The first player to guess correctly wins.
str: Doll Who adalah permainan papan deduksi di mana dua pemain mencoba menebak identitas karakter yang dipilih oleh lawan mereka. Setiap pemain memiliki papan dengan serangkaian karakter yang memiliki berbagai ciri. Dengan mengajukan pertanyaan ya atau tidak tentang fitur karakter (seperti apakah mereka memakai topi atau muncul di peta penitipan anak), pemain mengeliminasi opsi hingga mereka menemukan karakter lawan. Pemain pertama yang menebak dengan benar menang.

id: Only suitable for professionals, it starts at 08:00 and only has 3 effective clues, there are no photos or aids, some of the data is hidden, you have limited access to the map
str: Hanya cocok untuk profesional, dimulai pukul 08:00 dan hanya memiliki 3 petunjuk efektif, tidak ada foto atau alat bantu, beberapa data disembunyikan, akses Anda ke peta terbatas

id: You have all the clues and all the information about the dolls, but this is completely random for each doll.
str: Anda memiliki semua petunjuk dan semua informasi tentang boneka tersebut, tetapi ini sepenuhnya acak untuk setiap boneka.

id: Random mode but you're racing against the clock; find the doll before time runs out and earn trophies based on your speed.
str: Mode acak tetapi Anda berpacu dengan waktu;

id: Random but endless mode, you have a 3-minute timer to fix the case and there is a leaderboard of leaders
str: Mode acak namun tak ada habisnya, Anda memiliki pengatur waktu 3 menit untuk memperbaiki kasus dan ada papan peringkat pemimpin

id: As you unlock new levels, new ones will appear!
str: Saat Anda membuka level baru, level baru akan muncul!

id: One more step of difficulty, there are no extra clues, You can't see the names or list
str: Satu langkah lagi kesulitannya, tidak ada petunjuk tambahan, Anda tidak dapat melihat nama atau daftarnya

id: Expert mode, you start from 06:00, there are no extra clues and no photographs
str: Mode ahli, Anda mulai dari pukul 06:00, tidak ada petunjuk tambahan dan tidak ada foto

id: The standard difficulty for each player, all clues will be made at 08:00, you have the option to see the names of the dolls and the list of actions of the imposter
str: Kesulitan standar untuk setiap pemain, semua petunjuk akan dibuat pada pukul 08:00, Anda memiliki opsi untuk melihat nama-nama boneka dan daftar tindakan penipu

id: Your save game has been successfully restored, it may be wise to restart the game.
str: Save game Anda telah berhasil dipulihkan, mungkin bijaksana untuk memulai ulang game.

id: The backup has been successfully saved, if you want to restore it, just restart the game and you will see (restore previous save) in this menu.
str: Backup telah berhasil disimpan, jika ingin mengembalikannya cukup restart gamenya dan Anda akan melihat (restore save sebelumnya) di menu ini.

id: This is a beta version, it is advisable to make a copy of your saved game as there is a risk of losing such data. Want to make a copy?
str: Ini adalah versi beta, disarankan untuk membuat salinan dari game simpanan Anda karena ada risiko kehilangan data tersebut. Ingin membuat salinan?

id: An error occurred while displaying the server listing, please try again later.
str: Terjadi kesalahan saat menampilkan daftar server, silakan coba lagi nanti.

id: Ive created a more advanced guide that explores all aspects of Career Mode. If you need more help, I recommend you check it out; it will help you solve your future cases!
str: Saya telah membuat panduan lebih lanjut yang mengeksplorasi semua aspek Mode Karir. Jika Anda memerlukan bantuan lebih lanjut, saya sarankan Anda memeriksanya;

id: Did you understand the tutorial well?
str: Apakah Anda memahami tutorialnya dengan baik?

id: You have lost 75% for not discovering the impostor
str: Anda kehilangan 75% karena tidak menemukan si penipu

id: You have lost 90% of the entire reward due to missing photos.
str: Anda telah kehilangan 90% dari seluruh hadiah karena kehilangan foto.

id: For the changes to take effect, restart the game
str: Agar perubahan diterapkan, mulai ulang game

id: This option will only be available on Easy difficulty.
str: Opsi ini hanya akan tersedia pada tingkat kesulitan Mudah.

id: Number of photographs taken of dolls
You've earned the Employee of the Week medal!
str: Anda telah mendapatkan medali Karyawan Terbaik Minggu Ini!

id: You can now see this medal in your Employee of the Week chest!
str: Anda sekarang dapat melihat medali ini di peti Karyawan Minggu Ini!
